<p class="ql-align-justify">3种不同国家的椰子</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">做成原汁鲜甜汤底</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">海南文昌鸡皮脆肉嫩</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">得用上千的珐琅锅来煮</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">喝完这口汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">手里的奶茶都不香了</p>
